00:54:34,970 --> 00:54:36,500
我呢?
And for me?

736
00:54:36,510 --> 00:54:38,240
从今以后都照应你
From now on.

737
00:54:38,710 --> 00:54:40,170
我一直都在想念你
I missed you all this time.

738
00:54:40,180 --> 00:54:42,470
我也想念你 小妹妹
I missed you, too, cousin.

739
00:54:42,780 --> 00:54:45,770
我很怀念以前大家一起成长的时光
I missed growing up with all my cousins.

740
00:54:45,780 --> 00:54:48,640
没认识你之前我就想念你了
I didn't know you, and I missed you.

741
00:54:48,790 --> 00:54:53,510
你还记得当年我们父亲的事吗?
Do you remember stories about our fathers, the old days?

742
00:54:53,520 --> 00:54:55,690
记得 你想知道些什么?
Yeah. What do you want to know?

743
00:54:58,200 --> 00:55:00,260
山尼大伯是怎么样的人?
What was Sonny like?

744
00:55:02,230 --> 00:55:04,860
他是城里的风头人物
He was the prince of the city.

745
00:55:05,000 --> 00:55:06,630
他在我出生之前就死了
He died before I was born

746
00:55:06,640 --> 00:55:10,270
但我听过关于他的许多故事 他是个传奇
But I heard a million stories. He was a legend.

747
00:55:10,470 --> 00:55:12,670
那我爸爸呢?
What about my father?

748
00:55:12,680 --> 00:55:15,000
他是个伟大的人物
A great man, your father.

749
00:55:15,680 --> 00:55:18,610
他是个英雄 他拯救了整个家族
He's a hero. He saved the family.

750
00:55:19,920 --> 00:55:21,680
- 文森 - 什么?
- Vincent. - What?

751
00:55:21,690 --> 00:55:24,080
他有没有杀自己的亲兄弟?
Did he kill his own brother?

752
00:55:28,390 --> 00:55:30,660
没有
No.

753
00:55:32,300 --> 00:55:34,860
所以那些传言都是谎话?
So those are all lies?

754
00:55:38,340 --> 00:55:43,070
只是传言 知道吗?
Just stories, sweetheart. OK?

755
00:55:45,640 --> 00:55:48,000
知道了
OK.

756
00:55:48,580 --> 00:55:51,010
我相信你
I believe you.

757
00:55:51,550 --> 00:55:53,140
我很高兴你在我身边
I'm glad you're around.

758
00:55:53,150 --> 00:55:55,510
我也很高兴
I'm glad you're here too.

759
00:56:02,260 --> 00:56:04,290
堂哥
Cousin.

760
00:56:18,070 --> 00:56:21,800
我真想把札萨也带上来 然后把他推下去
I'd like to take Joey Zasa up for a ride in this and drop him.

761
00:56:21,810 --> 00:56:24,670
札萨算什么
Joey Zasa is nothing.

762
00:56:24,680 --> 00:56:27,070
不过是个微不足道的小跑腿
He's a small-time enforcer.

763
00:56:27,080 --> 00:56:29,980
也就吹吹牛 吓唬吓唬人 没什么
He bluffs, threats, but nothing.

764
00:56:29,990 --> 00:56:33,310
老远你就能知道他来了
You'll be able to see him coming a mile away.

765
00:56:33,320 --> 00:56:36,750
- 我们应该趁早杀了他以免... - 不行!
- We should kill him before he kills... - No!

766
00:56:39,060 --> 00:56:44,230
永远不要恨你的敌人 这会影响你的判断
Never hate your enemies. It affects your judgment.

767
00:56:51,710 --> 00:56:56,970
新泽西 亚特兰大城

768
00:56:59,620 --> 00:57:03,080
晚上好 柯里昂先生 很高兴再次见到你
Good evening. Nice to see you again, Mr. Corleone.

769
00:57:42,930 --> 00:57:47,320
我们相信你 让你来掌管我们赌场的钱
We trusted you to manage our money in the casinos.

770
00:57:47,330 --> 00:57:50,990
可还不到二十年 你就卖掉赌场
It's not even 20 years you sold the casinos

771
00:57:51,000 --> 00:57:53,230
帮我们大家都大赚了一笔
and you made fortunes for all of us.

772
00:57:53,240 --> 00:57:57,830
厉害啊柯里昂阁下!
Bravo, Don Corleone!

773
00:57:57,840 --> 00:57:59,800
过奖
Thank you.

774
00:57:59,810 --> 00:58:03,440
朋友们 我到这里来
Friends, I have come here

775
00:58:03,450 --> 00:58:08,080
是因为我们的共同事业已经结束了
because, our business together is done.

776
00:58:08,280 --> 00:58:10,040
我们都赚了大钱
We have prospered

777
00:58:10,050 --> 00:58:12,180
现在是时候
and now it is time for us

778
00:58:12,190 --> 00:58:16,050
解除我们之间的合作关系了
to dissolve the business relationship between us.

779
00:58:17,360 --> 00:58:19,120
到此为止
That's it.

780
00:58:19,130 --> 00:58:23,700
不过我有份小礼物
But I do have a little surprise

781
00:58:25,500 --> 00:58:28,330
各位在赌场所持的股份
Your shares in the casino

782
00:58:28,340 --> 00:58:30,140
我会免去所有程序
I thought I'd cut through all the red tape

783
00:58:30,150 --> 00:58:32,270
直接兑现
so you can get your money right away.

784
00:58:38,680 --> 00:58:41,240
五千万!
$50 million!

785
00:58:41,250 --> 00:58:44,040
每个人都不一样 按当初...
Not everybody gets the same. It depends on how much...

786
00:58:44,050 --> 00:58:47,010
- 没你的份儿 - 你资的额度及时间长短
- Nothing for you. - you invested and how long for.

787
00:58:47,020 --> 00:58:50,280
麦克 你真大方!
Michael, this is really generous!

788
00:58:50,290 --> 00:58:53,060
好极了
Oh, wonderful.

789
00:58:54,000 --> 00:58:55,620
谢谢
Grazier

790
00:58:55,630 --> 00:58:58,660
巴利西 你当初投了多少?
Hey, Parisi, how much did you invest?

791
00:58:58,740 --> 00:58:59,860
记不得了
I don't remember.

792
00:58:59,870 --> 00:59:02,570
上帝会保佑你的 麦克
Michael, you're blessed.

793
00:59:07,410 --> 00:59:10,970
我的家族担了大部分苦差事
My family has done much of the hard work

794
00:59:10,980 --> 00:59:13,580
冒了很多风险
taken many risks

795
00:59:14,350 --> 00:59:18,750
来为你们赚钱
all to make money for the rest of the families.

796
00:59:19,790 --> 00:59:22,820
各位都认识乔札萨
You all know Joey Zasa.

797
00:59:22,830 --> 00:59:26,320
我承认他是个大人物
He is, I admit, an important man.

798
00:59:26,330 --> 00:59:30,720
时代周刊封面登过他的照片
His picture is on the cover of the New York Times Magazine.

799
00:59:30,730 --> 00:59:36,030
绅士杂志还封他为最佳着装帮派人物
He gets the Esquire magazine award for the best-dressed gangster.

800
00:59:36,040 --> 00:59:41,230
各大报纸赞扬他 因为他雇用黑人
The newspapers praise him because he hires blacks into his family

801
00:59:41,240 --> 00:59:43,570
表现得那么宽厚
which shows he has a good heart

802
00:59:45,110 --> 00:59:49,340
他是个名人 天知道
He is famous. Who knows?

803
00:59:49,350 --> 00:59:51,310
也许有一天
Maybe one day

804
00:59:51,320 --> 00:59:54,820
他会让在做各位都成为名人
he will make all of you popular.

805
00:59:55,460 --> 00:59:56,720
不错
It's true.

806
00:59:56,730 --> 01:00:00,650
我讲究穿着和仪容
I make more of a bella figura.

807
01:00:00,660 --> 01:00:02,520
这是我的天性
That is my nature.

808
01:00:02,530 --> 01:00:07,660
但我也想让自己的事业合法化
But I also want to make a move into legitimate enterprises.

809
01:00:07,670 --> 01:00:10,370
想要教皇给我封勋
I'd like to get a little pin from the pope.

810
01:00:10,640 --> 01:00:13,600
不错 我雇佣黑人
Sure, I take the blacks

811
01:00:13,610 --> 01:00:16,070
甚至是南美籍人
and the Spanish into my family

812
01:00:16,080 --> 01:00:20,240
因为这里是美国
because that's America.

813
01:00:20,250 --> 01:00:25,350
你敢担保他们不在我们的地盘上贩毒?
And you guarantee that they don't deal drugs in those neighborhoods.

814
01:00:25,360 --> 01:00:27,480
这个我不担保
I don't guarantee that.

815
01:00:27,490 --> 01:00:31,560
我只担保谁贩毒我杀谁
I guarantee I'll kill anybody who does.

816
01:00:34,730 --> 01:00:38,120
我来劝劝他 我来
Let me talk to him. Let me talk to him.

817
01:00:38,130 --> 01:00:40,430
谁能拒绝艾图贝洛阁下?
Who can refuse Don Altobello?

818
01:00:40,440 --> 01:00:41,830
乔
Joe

819
01:00:41,840 --> 01:00:43,500
不用!
No!

820
01:00:43,510 --> 01:00:44,760
我告诉你们
I say to all of you

821
01:00:44,770 --> 01:00:50,040
今天 你们对我毫无尊重
I have been treated this day with no respect.

822
01:00:50,050 --> 01:00:52,170
我替你们所有人赚钱
I've earned you all money.

823
01:00:52,180 --> 01:00:54,040
我让你们发财
I've made you rich.

824
01:00:54,050 --> 01:00:55,540
自己只要求少许
and I asked for little.

825
01:00:55,550 --> 01:00:58,240
好啊你们不给?
Good. You will not give?

826
01:00:58,250 --> 01:01:00,750
那我就自己拿
I'll take.

827
01:01:00,760 --> 01:01:03,620
至于柯里昂阁下…
As for Don Corleone

828
01:01:03,630 --> 01:01:07,450
今天他讲得很清楚
well he makes it, very clear to me today

829
01:01:07,460 --> 01:01:11,200
摆明与我为敌
that he is my enemy.

830
01:01:13,270 --> 01:01:16,090
你们必须在我们两个当中选一个
You must choose between us.

831
01:01:19,080 --> 01:01:24,170
乔 不要这样 乔
Hey Joey, no, Joey, no, Joey

832
01:01:24,180 --> 01:01:27,710
大家可以坐下来谈
We can reason together.

833
01:01:28,020 --> 01:01:31,910
拜托 麦克
Michael, Michael

834
01:01:31,920 --> 01:01:33,450
我们慢慢谈
let's agree, huh?

835
01:01:33,460 --> 01:01:35,950
他根本不知道自己刚才
He doesn't know what he's

836
01:01:35,960 --> 01:01:38,060
不行
No, no no.

837
01:01:42,330 --> 01:01:46,090
麦克 到处都有消息说
Uh, Michael, Michael. The news is everywhere.

838
01:01:46,100 --> 01:01:50,360
你已经控制了"屹立"
Everyone is saying that, you control Immobiliare.

839
01:01:50,370 --> 01:01:54,100
"屹立"已经在秘鲁洗黑钱了
Immobiliare already is laundering money in Peru

840
01:01:54,110 --> 01:01:56,600
还有拿骚 我们都知道
and Nassau. We know that.

841
01:01:56,610 --> 01:01:58,780
麦克 我们朋友也做了四十年了
Listen to me. We've been friends for 40 years.

842
01:01:58,790 --> 01:02:01,110
我们也应该沾一点光
We should wet our beaks a little, huh?

843
01:02:01,120 --> 01:02:03,810
我们想和你一起做生意
We want to do business with you.

844
01:02:03,820 --> 01:02:09,180
- 好... - 用圣水洗净我们的钱...
- That's right... - We can wash our money clean in the holy water of...

845
01:02:16,130 --> 01:02:20,390
暗杀 快走 跟我来 快走!
It's a hit. Let's go. Follow me. Let's get outta here!

846
01:02:38,450 --> 01:02:40,080
- 我的外套! - 不要外套了
- My coat! - Forget your coat.

847
01:02:40,090 --> 01:02:43,950
这是我的幸运外套! 幸运外套!
It's my lucky coat! It's my lucky coat!

848
01:02:50,600 --> 01:02:52,460
跟在我后面!
Stay right behind me!

849
01:03:08,050 --> 01:03:10,410
麦克 走这边!
Mikey, this way!

850
01:03:17,660 --> 01:03:22,230
札萨 你这混帐东西!
Zasa you son of bitch!

851
01:03:42,150 --> 01:03:44,080
走 我们赶紧离开
Come on, we're outta here.

852
01:04:16,690 --> 01:04:19,350
- 你干得很好 - 谢谢
- You did good. - Grazier.

853
01:04:19,390 --> 01:04:22,555
所有老头目几乎全死了
The old Dons were pretty much wiped out.

854
01:04:22,590 --> 01:04:27,020
幸存下来的也都改投乔札萨了
The ones that survived made deals with Joey Zasa.

855
01:04:27,030 --> 01:04:28,220
艾图贝洛呢?
Don Altobello?

856
01:04:28,230 --> 01:04:29,620
他活下来了
He survived.

857
01:04:29,630 --> 01:04:32,490
在他女儿斯达坦岛上的家里
He's with his daughters now in Staten Island.

858
01:04:32,500 --> 01:04:35,600
他说要退隐 回西西里
Says he's gonna retire to Sicily.

859
01:04:36,510 --> 01:04:42,000
没人撑腰 札萨决不会来这一手
Joey Zasa would never pull something like this without the backing.

860
01:04:42,010 --> 01:04:45,170
他只会听人做事 其他什么都不会
He's just muscle. He's an enforcer. He's nothing.

861
01:04:45,180 --> 01:04:47,610
用直升机行刺 他还想不出来这招
He doesn't have the wit for that helicopter attack.

862
01:04:47,620 --> 01:04:52,150
他甚至都没那点野心和胆量敢消灭全帮
He doesn't even have the ambition to wipe out the whole commission.

863
01:04:52,160 --> 01:04:56,360
我说我们要反击 也弄死他!
I say we hit back and take Zasa out!

864
01:05:00,560 --> 01:05:03,350
决不能让别人知道你在想什么
Never let anyone know what you're thinking.

865
01:05:11,410 --> 01:05:15,170
传话给乔札萨
Well, let's get a message to Joey Zasa.

866
01:05:17,610 --> 01:05:20,310
对于他所做的事情 我很敬佩
I respect what he's done.

867
01:05:21,050 --> 01:05:24,480
长江后浪推前浪 真很正常
The new overthrows the old. It's natural.

868
01:05:24,490 --> 01:05:26,720
你怎么能跟这种家伙做生意?
How can you do business with this guy?

869
01:05:29,460 --> 01:05:31,180
我现在首先是个生意人
I'm a businessman, first and foremost.

870
01:05:31,190 --> 01:05:33,790
不想跟他再起冲突
I want no further conflict with him.

871
01:05:33,800 --> 01:05:36,320
告诉他 我决定他的死活
You tell him from me that he can live or he can die.

872
01:05:36,330 --> 01:05:39,070
文森 住口!
Vincent, will you shut up!

873
01:05:56,750 --> 01:05:58,450
好了
That's it.

874
01:06:00,390 --> 01:06:05,220
乔札萨一个人干不出这种事
He can't be doing this alone.

875
01:06:08,560 --> 01:06:10,860
我刚以为自己退出江湖了
Just when I thought I was out,

876
01:06:10,870 --> 01:06:13,800
又被拖回去
they pull me back in.

877
01:06:21,880 --> 01:06:28,880
真正的大敌还没有露面呢
Our true enemy has not yet shown his face.

878
01:06:31,320 --> 01:06:35,780
麦克! 麦克!
Michael! Michael!

879
01:06:35,790 --> 01:06:37,560
挺住!
No!

880
01:06:39,560 --> 01:06:40,650
他有没有带药?
Has he taken his medicine?

881
01:06:40,660 --> 01:06:42,450
我不知道他吃什么药
I don't know what he took.

882
01:06:46,040 --> 01:06:51,300
- 我能喘气了 - 快叫医生
- I've got my wind back. - Call a doctor.

883
01:06:51,310 --> 01:06:53,270
- 快去 快去! - 文森!
- Run, run! - Vincent!

884
01:06:53,280 --> 01:06:57,540
快奔向雷电 雷声伤不了任何人
Run at thunderbolt. Thunder can't hurt.

885
01:06:57,550 --> 01:06:59,910
声音伤不了任何东西
Harmless noise.

886
01:06:59,920 --> 01:07:02,080
胡说八道
Bullshit.

887
01:07:02,180 --> 01:07:05,540
他妈的老狐狸
You deceitful old fuck.

888
01:07:05,550 --> 01:07:08,850
老艾 你个天杀的老狐狸!
Altobello, you fuck!

889
01:07:10,860 --> 01:07:12,650
弗雷德!
Fredo!

890
01:07:13,030 --> 01:07:15,460
弗雷德!
Fredo!

891
01:07:38,450 --> 01:07:41,810
天啊爸
Oh, God. Dad.

892
01:07:45,760 --> 01:07:47,430
我通知凯!
I'll call Kay.

893
01:07:57,810 --> 01:07:58,970
先生 晚上好
Good evening, sir.

894
01:07:58,980 --> 01:08:00,770
能不能停一下? 我马上回来
Can we wait here? I'll be right back.

895
01:08:00,780 --> 01:08:02,340
好的 先生!
Certainly, sir.

896
01:08:08,380 --> 01:08:12,550
你说有紧急事故 哈里森先生
Mr. Harrison, you said it was urgent.

897
01:08:12,560 --> 01:08:15,080
你来告解过吗?
Have you come to confess your sins?

898
01:08:15,090 --> 01:08:17,450
柯里昂先生因糖尿病中风
Michael Corleone suffered a diabetic stroke.

899
01:08:17,460 --> 01:08:19,890
我想见报之前应先通知你
I thought you should know that before you read it in the papers.

900
01:08:20,700 --> 01:08:22,720
他现在昏迷不醒
He's in a coma on the critical list.

901
01:08:22,730 --> 01:08:25,890
我来这里是为了确保我们的交易将不受任何影响
I'm here to insist the deal goes through in any event.

902
01:08:25,900 --> 01:08:28,830
教皇的日子不多了
The pope has not much time left.

903
01:08:29,170 --> 01:08:33,470
我跟你一样处境为难
So, as you, I am in a difficult position.

904
01:08:33,480 --> 01:08:36,840
我们得尽早争取核准
We have to ratify this deal as soon as possible.

905
01:08:37,550 --> 01:08:39,570
这一点我们有共识
We have an understanding.

906
01:08:39,580 --> 01:08:41,350
很好
Good.

907
01:08:41,680 --> 01:08:42,880
我现在要去医院
I'm going to the hospital.

908
01:08:42,890 --> 01:08:44,910
我会为柯里昂先生祈祷
I'll pray for Mr. Corleone.

909
01:08:44,920 --> 01:08:46,850
谢谢你
Thank you.

910
01:08:50,190 --> 01:08:51,950
我们都会为柯里昂先生祈福
Our thoughts are with Mr. Corleone.

911
01:08:51,960 --> 01:08:53,730
谢谢你神父!
Thank you, Father.

912
01:08:56,630 --> 01:09:01,530
如柯里昂一死 内幕会揭开
Everything will be out in the open if Corleone dies.

913
01:09:01,600 --> 01:09:04,460
祈求我们能有更多的时间吧 凯斯济
Pray for time, Keinszig.

914
01:09:04,470 --> 01:09:10,680
这是从我对永恒的长久思考中养成的习惯
A habit born of, a long contemplation of eternity.

915
01:09:15,790 --> 01:09:17,280
文森 算了
Just forget about it, Vinnie

916
01:09:17,290 --> 01:09:19,710
为什么算了? 这很简单
