班甸奴阁下 我的老朋友
Don Bendino, my old friend.

1100
01:26:22,650 --> 01:26:24,440
我带你们来这里
I wanted to bring you here

1101
01:26:24,450 --> 01:26:26,210
好让我的老朋友及庇护人
so that my old friend and protector

1102
01:26:26,220 --> 01:26:28,310
汤马西诺阁下
Don Tommasino

1103
01:26:28,320 --> 01:26:30,350
给我们出主意
could advise us.

1104
01:26:30,520 --> 01:26:34,820
汤马西诺阁下 你以为老艾如何?
Don Tommasino, what do you think about Altobello?

1105
01:26:36,730 --> 01:26:38,920
他是个聪明人
A very talented man.

1106
01:26:38,930 --> 01:26:40,590
维持了我们西西里人
He has kept the peace between our Sicilian

1107
01:26:40,600 --> 01:26:43,860
与美国朋友之间的和平
and American friends.

1108
01:26:43,870 --> 01:26:46,540
讲道理的高手
The saint of reason.

1109
01:26:48,480 --> 01:26:51,040
亚特兰大城里的那次血洗行动
The bloodbath in Atlantic City,

1110
01:26:51,050 --> 01:26:52,740
把纽约城搞得鸡飞狗跳
left New York a mess.

1111
01:26:52,750 --> 01:26:56,140
本来札萨想控制这个艰难的时局
Now, Joey Zasa at least was running a very tight ship,

1112
01:26:56,150 --> 01:27:00,110
现在他死了 我们必须介入
but now that he's out of the picture, we're obligated to step in.

1113
01:27:00,120 --> 01:27:01,880
又回去
Step back in.

1114
01:27:01,890 --> 01:27:03,050
我们不去 迟早华人
If we don't, the Chinese,

1115
01:27:03,060 --> 01:27:04,970
或者哥伦比亚人会趁虚而入
the Colombians will.

1116
01:27:05,005 --> 01:27:06,880
柯里昂家族从不贩毒
The Corleone's left drugs,

1117
01:27:06,890 --> 01:27:11,030
所以纽约弱 巴勒摩强
so New York is weak, and Palermo is strong

1118
01:27:11,370 --> 01:27:13,260
你丢下的地方
Your enemies always get strong

1119
01:27:13,270 --> 01:27:15,590
敌人就能乘机坐大
on what you leave behind

1120
01:27:15,840 --> 01:27:18,005
汤马西诺阁下
Don Tommasino

1121
01:27:18,040 --> 01:27:23,500
谁可能指使那场屠杀
who could give the order for that massacre

1122
01:27:24,550 --> 01:27:28,810
而且还能在梵蒂冈的交易上施压?
and still pressure the Vatican deal?

1123
01:27:28,820 --> 01:27:30,740
只有鲁加西
Only Lucchesi

1124
01:27:30,750 --> 01:27:34,540
能在黑白两道都吃得开
can reach between these two worlds.

1125
01:27:35,620 --> 01:27:39,360
我们的船必须朝同一个方向航行
Our ships must all sail in the same direction

1126
01:27:40,630 --> 01:27:43,790
几百年来意大利政界都有这种人
Italian politics have had these kind of men for centuries.

1127
01:27:43,800 --> 01:27:46,660
他们 才是真正的黑手党
They're, the true Mafia

1128
01:27:46,670 --> 01:27:49,960
大主教和梵蒂冈银行的事是个大问题
The Archbishop and the Vatican bank, that's the big problem.

1129
01:27:49,970 --> 01:27:51,760
是一样的
They're the same problem

1130
01:27:51,770 --> 01:27:54,975
他们之间有勾结
B.J., they're connected.

1131
01:27:55,010 --> 01:27:58,280
大主教有些权贵朋友
The Archbishop has very powerful friends.

1132
01:28:00,350 --> 01:28:02,370
他们会全力维护他
They totally protect him.

1133
01:28:02,380 --> 01:28:07,210
教会方面 我们有谁能够投靠吗?
Is there someone in the church we can turn to?

1134
01:28:07,220 --> 01:28:09,650
德高望重的人
Someone we can tell our problem to.

1135
01:28:11,760 --> 01:28:14,380
红衣主教龙巴度
Cardinal Lamberto.

1136
01:28:14,390 --> 01:28:17,790
为人和善睿智
A wise and good man

1137
01:28:17,800 --> 01:28:19,720
极有影响力
very influential.

1138
01:28:19,730 --> 01:28:23,870
他会见你的
He will see you.

1139
01:28:27,780 --> 01:28:30,600
好 我会去拜见龙巴度枢机
Bene. I will go see this Cardinal Lamberto

1140
01:28:30,610 --> 01:28:34,110
看看这件事能不能以文明的方式了解
and see if we can work things out in a civilized way

1141
01:28:35,420 --> 01:28:38,040
就算你遵守协约
You honor your agreements

1142
01:28:38,050 --> 01:28:40,810
可是你要对付的那帮人全是些无赖
But these people you're dealing with are crooks

1143
01:28:40,820 --> 01:28:43,250
他们是不会守信的
they have no honor.

1144
01:28:45,430 --> 01:28:47,420
一切由我作主
My word is final.

1145
01:28:57,370 --> 01:29:02,070
政治与犯罪本来就是一回事
Politics and crime. They're the same thing

1146
01:29:18,030 --> 01:29:21,890
好! 精彩!
Bravo! Bravo, Bravo!

1147
01:29:23,900 --> 01:29:26,220
今天我邀请各位到此
I have invited you all here

1148
01:29:26,230 --> 01:29:31,130
是为了庆祝我的儿子首次登台演出
to celebrate, my son's first appearance in an opera house

1149
01:29:31,170 --> 01:29:35,330
他将于三周后
He will be appearing, in about three weeks

1150
01:29:35,340 --> 01:29:39,070
在玛西摩剧院登台
in the Theatre Maximo

1151
01:29:39,080 --> 01:29:41,470
演出"乡间骑士"
in the opera, Cavalleria Rusticana.

1152
01:29:41,480 --> 01:29:44,340
爸爸 是乡间骑士
It's Cavalleria Rusticana dad.

1153
01:29:44,350 --> 01:29:47,980
骑士看来我买错歌剧票了
Cavalleria. I think I've got tickets to the wrong opera.

1154
01:29:48,290 --> 01:29:49,810
我在纽约待得太久了
I've been in New York too long.

1155
01:29:49,820 --> 01:29:53,480
大家都会收到门票
Anyway, you will all receive tickets.

1156
01:29:53,490 --> 01:29:55,150
多多捧场啊
So come on down.

1157
01:29:55,160 --> 01:29:56,620
爸 我有一份礼物给你
Uh, dad, I've got a present for you

1158
01:30:01,170 --> 01:30:03,590
从柯里昂乡城流传而来
It comes from the town of Corleone and uh,

1159
01:30:03,600 --> 01:30:05,740
是道地的西西里歌谣
it's authentic Sicilian

1160
01:30:08,740 --> 01:30:11,010
我 是为你学的
And uh, I learned it for you

1161
01:31:39,670 --> 01:31:43,830
她又漂亮又善良 我爱她
She was, wonderful, beautiful. I loved her.

1162
01:31:43,840 --> 01:31:45,700
然而她死了
And then she died.

1163
01:31:46,240 --> 01:31:48,940
我的亲信保镖
My trusted bodyguard

1164
01:31:49,680 --> 01:31:52,540
在我车上装炸弹
planted a bomb in my car

1165
01:31:52,980 --> 01:31:55,210
她却在我之前驾驶那辆车
she drove it before I did.

1166
01:31:56,720 --> 01:32:00,410
为什么在这么美丽的地方却充满了暴力?
Why is such a beautiful country, so violent?

1167
01:32:00,420 --> 01:32:02,010
这是历史渊源
History.

1168
01:32:02,020 --> 01:32:04,240
妈妈告诉我说她以前最担心的
You know, mom was telling me about the old days,

1169
01:32:04,250 --> 01:32:06,650
就是怕考试不及格
when her biggest worry was just passing exams

1170
01:32:06,660 --> 01:32:08,650
没错
Yes it was, then.

1171
01:32:08,660 --> 01:32:10,620
现在我为你担心
I worry about you now.

1172
01:32:10,630 --> 01:32:15,960
玛莉 你真是个心地善良的孩子 你总是这样
Oh Mary. Mary you're such a warm-hearted girl, you always were.

1173
01:32:15,970 --> 01:32:17,830
我爱我的家人
I love my family.

1174
01:32:18,010 --> 01:32:20,000
甚至是你的堂兄文森?
Even your cousin Vincent?

1175
01:32:23,340 --> 01:32:25,800
我是真心爱他
I really love him.

1176
01:32:26,980 --> 01:32:28,770
他是你的近亲
He's your first cousin.

1177
01:32:28,780 --> 01:32:30,980
那我更加爱他
Then I love him first.

1178
01:32:31,250 --> 01:32:34,750
玛莉 你不能见他
Mary, you can't see him.

1179
01:32:34,760 --> 01:32:37,720
不要再见他了
Just don't see him any more

1180
01:32:37,920 --> 01:32:42,390
他说的对 太危险了
He's right. it's too dangerous

1181
01:32:43,700 --> 01:32:45,060
玛丽 听我说
Mary, listen to me.

1182
01:32:45,070 --> 01:32:48,430
你不能再见他了 不能以那种关系
You can't see him anymore. Not in that fashion.

1183
01:32:48,440 --> 01:32:50,000
不要
No.

1184
01:32:50,900 --> 01:32:54,500
- 答应我 - 不要
- Please promise me - No.

1185
01:32:54,510 --> 01:32:55,870
这件事你一定要答应!
Obey me on this Mary!

1186
01:32:55,880 --> 01:32:57,770
不要 爸爸!
No, dad!

1187
01:33:02,150 --> 01:33:04,350
玛莉是个聪明的孩子
Mary's smart, dad

1188
01:33:04,750 --> 01:33:07,080
她会明白的
she'll understand eventually.

1189
01:33:29,440 --> 01:33:33,270
美丽的堂妹 我的宝贝

1190
01:33:43,790 --> 01:33:44,880
你要见我?
You wanted to see me?

1191
01:33:44,890 --> 01:33:46,560
是的
Yeah.

1192
01:33:46,830 --> 01:33:49,220
- 我要你去办件事 - 好的
- I want you to do something for me. - Okay.

1193
01:33:49,230 --> 01:33:50,890
这很危险
It's dangerous.

1194
01:33:52,000 --> 01:33:55,990
好 我做 要我做什么?
Good. I'm in. What do you need?

1195
01:33:56,000 --> 01:33:59,140
我要你投靠艾图贝洛
I want you to sell your soul to Don Altobello.

1196
01:33:59,710 --> 01:34:01,560
背叛我
To betray me.

1197
01:34:05,050 --> 01:34:06,810
他不可能相信我 这里
He'll never believe me. Here.

1198
01:34:08,010 --> 01:34:11,220
- 那要看情形 - 坐下
- That depends. - Sit down.

1199
01:34:13,550 --> 01:34:15,340
我有办法
I have an idea.

1200
01:34:16,560 --> 01:34:21,090
你去探听老艾的关系攀到了多高
See if you can learn how high Altobello is connected.

1201
01:34:24,300 --> 01:34:26,960
安排一次见面
Arrange a meeting.

1202
01:34:28,540 --> 01:34:31,800
你说你对我忠心耿耿
You say how devoted you are to me.

1203
01:34:31,840 --> 01:34:34,230
再告诉他你的问题
Tell him your problems.

1204
01:34:34,240 --> 01:34:36,570
向他求助
You ask for his help.

1205
01:34:36,580 --> 01:34:38,340
什么问题?
What problems?

1206
01:34:39,180 --> 01:34:41,950
说你想和我女儿私奔
That you want to run away with my daughter.

1207
01:34:42,620 --> 01:34:47,750
又怕这样会与我反目成仇
Only you know that if you do, I will become your enemy.

1208
01:34:51,630 --> 01:34:54,090
你知道我决不会这么做的 麦克叔
You know I'd never do that, Uncle Mike.

1209
01:34:54,130 --> 01:34:55,860
我知道
I know.

1210
01:34:56,400 --> 01:35:01,760
你求老艾来找我为你们说情
You ask Altobello to speak to me. To further the marriage.

1211
01:35:01,770 --> 01:35:03,930
你们毕竟是堂兄妹
You're cousins

1212
01:35:03,940 --> 01:35:07,460
麦克一向都保守
Michael was always a little old fashioned.

1213
01:35:07,470 --> 01:35:11,410
跟他说你不愿跟我做合法生意
Explain to him how, you can never be part of my, legitimate world.

1214
01:35:11,420 --> 01:35:13,540
要自立门户
That you want your own family.

1215
01:35:13,550 --> 01:35:15,780
我能接下札萨的摊子
straighten out with Joey Zasa

1216
01:35:18,220 --> 01:35:22,150
如果你能够说服他
If you could use your friendship to persuade him

1217
01:35:22,160 --> 01:35:25,120
我会永远记得你的恩情
I would be indebted to you forever.

1218
01:35:26,930 --> 01:35:28,890
柯里昂家的人
A Corleone

1219
01:35:28,900 --> 01:35:31,890
都非常重情谊
knows the value of such a friend.

1220
01:35:32,430 --> 01:35:35,460
那你肯为我做事?
So, then, you would work for me?

1221
01:35:35,900 --> 01:35:42,660
是
Si.

1222
01:35:43,640 --> 01:35:45,400
记住
Remember

1223
01:35:45,410 --> 01:35:49,540
假如他暗示要你背叛我
if he hints that he wants you to betray me

1224
01:35:49,550 --> 01:35:51,070
你要装出收到侮辱的样子
get insulted.

1225
01:35:51,080 --> 01:35:53,780
他只是试探你
Because that's his trap.

1226
01:35:59,990 --> 01:36:04,090
你没有告诉我所有实情 文森
You're not telling me the whole truth, Vincenzo.

1227
01:36:06,270 --> 01:36:13,530
只要麦克一死 一切不都是由那个女孩儿继承?
Isn't it true, with Michael gone, the girl controls everything?

1228
01:36:16,080 --> 01:36:18,640
你别扯上那女孩
You leave the girl out of this.

1229
01:36:18,650 --> 01:36:22,610
当然 你爱她 她也爱你
Of course, you love her. And she loves you.

1230
01:36:42,500 --> 01:36:46,600
我猜中了吧 文森
I guessed it Vincenzo, huh?

1231
01:36:46,940 --> 01:36:50,230
你是位智者 艾图贝洛阁下
You're a wise man, Don Altobello.

1232
01:36:50,240 --> 01:36:53,040
有好多事我要跟你学习
I'm going to be learning a lot from you.

1233
01:36:53,050 --> 01:36:57,650
最富有的人是拥有最多权贵朋友的人
The richest man is the one with the most powerful friends.

1234
01:36:59,020 --> 01:37:03,150
我有责任为你介绍
It's my duty to make the introductions.

1235
01:37:08,530 --> 01:37:10,590
鲁加西阁下
Don Lucchesi

1236
01:37:13,270 --> 01:37:17,760
老艾说你是个坚强的人
Don Altobello tells me you have good character, strong

1237
01:37:17,770 --> 01:37:19,200
是个值得人尊重的人
a man of respect.

1238
01:37:19,210 --> 01:37:23,030
这就是令札萨长眠的英雄
This is the hero who put Joey Zasa in his grave.

1239
01:37:23,040 --> 01:37:24,770
早认识他
If we'd known of his existence

1240
01:37:24,780 --> 01:37:27,500
我们就不会支持札萨了
we would never have backed Joey.

1241
01:37:27,510 --> 01:37:30,040
没有人会愿意的
No one wants another Joe

1242
01:37:31,480 --> 01:37:34,340
我们交个朋友吧
Let me be your friend.

1243
01:37:34,350 --> 01:37:37,380
最坚强的人也要交朋友
Even the strongest man needs friends.

1244
01:37:37,390 --> 01:37:39,160
这太荣幸了
I'm flattered.

1245
01:37:39,960 --> 01:37:42,890
但鲁西尼阁下你是金融政治人物
But you're a man of finance and politics, Don Lucchesi

1246
01:37:42,900 --> 01:37:45,260
那些事我都不懂
these are things I don't understand.

1247
01:37:46,130 --> 01:37:48,490
你知道怎么用枪吗?
You understand guns?

1248
01:37:48,500 --> 01:37:50,960
金融就是一把枪
Finance is a gun.

1249
01:37:50,970 --> 01:37:53,060
政治
Politics

1250
01:37:53,070 --> 01:37:56,740
就是知道适时扣扳机
is knowing when to pull the trigger.

1251
01:37:59,810 --> 01:38:01,710
我要做些什么?
How can I help?

1252
01:38:06,520 --> 01:38:09,350
追求和平的人总是受到赐福
Blessed is the peacemaker

1253
01:38:09,360 --> 01:38:12,480
因为他可以被称为是神的儿子
for he can be called a child of God.

1254
01:38:12,490 --> 01:38:17,090
- 懂说一点意大利语吗? - 懂
- Can you speak Italian well? - Yes.

1255
01:38:37,880 --> 01:38:40,550
汤马西诺阁下的轮椅
The wheelchair, for Don Tommasino.

1256
01:38:48,430 --> 01:38:52,090
这笔交易我托给了大主教
I trusted this business arrangement with the archbishop.

1257
01:38:52,100 --> 01:38:57,330
我那么相信他 相信他的诚实
I trusted him. I was sure his honesty was beyond a doubt.

1258
01:38:57,340 --> 01:39:02,670
但现在 我完全被骗了
But, as you see, I'm now the victim of a swindle.

1259
01:39:02,680 --> 01:39:04,630
他一直在拖延着我
He's stalling me.

1260
01:39:04,640 --> 01:39:08,740
巨额的钱财都到了政界高层手里
Vast money have gone to the pezzonovante in high political places

1261
01:39:08,750 --> 01:39:11,710
而梵蒂冈银行为其做担保人
and the Vatican Bank is the guarantor.

1262
01:39:11,720 --> 01:39:14,380
如过你说的话属实
If uh, what you say is true

1263
01:39:14,390 --> 01:39:17,820
这将是个大丑闻
there will be a great scandal.

1264
01:39:19,160 --> 01:39:20,750
你看这块石头
Look at this stone.

1265
01:39:20,760 --> 01:39:24,150
它泡在水里已经很久了
It has been lying in the water for a very long time

1266
01:39:24,160 --> 01:39:29,030
水却仍然没有能够浸透它
but the water has not penetrated it.

1267
01:39:31,870 --> 01:39:33,540
你看
Look.

1268
01:39:34,270 --> 01:39:36,700
还是干的
Perfectly dry.

1269
01:39:37,110 --> 01:39:39,740
欧洲人也是这样
The same thing has happened to men in Europe.

1270
01:39:39,750 --> 01:39:44,640
多少个世纪以来 他们一直受基督教教诲
For centuries they have been surrounded by Christianity

1271
01:39:44,650 --> 01:39:47,440
但基督却仍然没能进入他们的心里
but Christ has not penetrated.

1272
01:39:47,450 --> 01:39:52,020
不能与他们在生活中相伴
Christ doesn't breathe within them.

1273
01:39:54,390 --> 01:39:55,520
这是怎么回事?
What's happened?

1274
01:39:55,530 --> 01:39:59,920
能不能 给我点甜的东西?
Is it possible, that you could get me something sweet?

1275
01:39:59,930 --> 01:40:03,100
柳橙汁 随便什么 糖果
Orange juice, anything, candy.

1276
01:40:06,040 --> 01:40:09,240
我有糖尿病
Trouble with diabetes.

1277
01:40:12,050 --> 01:40:14,640
血糖一定要保持低水平
Blood sugar levels must be low.

1278
01:40:14,650 --> 01:40:17,210
我了解
I understand.

1279
01:40:39,340 --> 01:40:42,570
压力一大 有时候就这样
When I'm under stress sometimes this happens.

1280
01:40:43,210 --> 01:40:45,200
我了解
I understand.

1281
01:40:46,810 --> 01:40:49,010
来见你
I come to you

1282
01:40:49,180 --> 01:40:52,110
说这种敏感的事
on such a delicate matter

1283
01:40:53,490 --> 01:40:56,910
指控大主教
accusations against your Archbishop

1284
01:40:56,920 --> 01:40:59,750
对我而言太难受
was difficult for me.

1285
01:40:59,760 --> 01:41:02,020
精神收到折磨
The mind suffers

1286
01:41:02,030 --> 01:41:06,030
身体自然不好
and the body, cries out.

1287
01:41:08,700 --> 01:41:13,560
的确如此
That's true.

1288
01:41:14,210 --> 01:41:19,210
你要不要做告解?
Would you like, to make your confession?

1289
01:41:25,050 --> 01:41:27,250
阁下
Your Eminence

1290
01:41:27,550 --> 01:41:33,320
我 我 很久没有做告解了
I'm uh, I'm uh, it's been so long,

1291
01:41:33,330 --> 01:41:37,820
我不 不 不知道从哪里...
I wouldn't, wouldn't, wouldn't know where to uh...

1292
01:41:37,830 --> 01:41:41,100
都有三十年了
it's been thirty years

1293
01:41:41,200 --> 01:41:45,300
我也许会耽误你很久
I'd, I'd, I'd use up too much of your time, I think.

1294
01:41:45,310 --> 01:41:49,270
拯救灵魂 我总是有时间的
I always have time to save souls.

1295
01:41:50,810 --> 01:41:53,600
我想 我已经罪无可赦
Well, I'm, I'm beyond redemption.

1296
01:42:03,490 --> 01:42:08,420
这里的教士也会向我告解
I hear the confessions of my own priests here.

1297
01:42:08,430 --> 01:42:12,760
有时候告解的心情已到极致
Sometimes the desire to confess is overwhelming

1298
01:42:12,770 --> 01:42:15,860
我们就要把握时机
and we must seize the moment.

1299
01:42:19,740 --> 01:42:22,170
假如我没有悔意
What is the point of confessing

1300
01:42:22,180 --> 01:42:26,000
告解有什么用?
if I don't repent?

1301
01:42:26,010 --> 01:42:29,470
我听说你精打细算
I hear you are a practical man

1302
01:42:29,480 --> 01:42:32,950
你认为告解会有什么损失吗?
What have you got to lose, huh?

1303
01:42:43,300 --> 01:42:45,220
说吧
Go on.

1304
01:42:51,540 --> 01:42:53,960
我
I

1305
01:42:54,110 --> 01:42:56,600
对妻子不忠
betrayed my wife.

1306
01:42:57,710 --> 01:43:00,070
说下去 孩子
Go on, my son.

1307
01:43:04,950 --> 01:43:07,190
背叛了自己的心
I betrayed myself.

1308
01:43:09,660 --> 01:43:11,750
我曾经杀过人
I killed men.

1309
01:43:15,360 --> 01:43:18,190
也曾令手下去杀人
And I ordered men to be killed.

1310
01:43:19,270 --> 01:43:22,860
接着说 孩子 接着说
Go on, my son, go on

1311
01:43:26,670 --> 01:43:29,410
这根本没用
It's useless.

1312
01:43:30,780 --> 01:43:33,340
说吧 孩子
Go on, my son.

1313
01:43:34,150 --> 01:43:36,180
我杀了
I killed

1314
01:43:40,350 --> 01:43:43,880
我让人杀了我的兄弟
I ordered the death of my brother.

1315
01:43:44,060 --> 01:43:46,950
他伤害了我
He injured me.

1316
01:43:47,460 --> 01:43:51,160
我杀了我母亲的儿子
I killed my mother's son.

1317
01:43:51,360 --> 01:43:55,400
我杀了自己的同胞兄弟
I killed my mother's son.

1318
01:44:04,110 --> 01:44:06,470
你的确罪大恶极
Your sins are terrible

1319
01:44:06,480 --> 01:44:10,270
因此你身心遭受苦痛
and it is just that you suffer

1320
01:44:10,280 --> 01:44:13,810
你的人生仍可获得救赎
Your life could be redeemed

1321
01:44:13,820 --> 01:44:16,110
但我知道你不相信
but I know that you don't believe that.

1322
01:44:16,120 --> 01:44:18,450
你也不会有所改变
You will not change.

1323
01:44:41,550 --> 01:44:44,870
教皇保禄六世
Pope Paul VI

1324
01:44:44,880 --> 01:44:50,410
罗马天主教廷至尊
the Supreme Pontiff of the Roman Catholic Church

1325
01:44:50,420 --> 01:44:54,650
于昨晚九时四十分辞世
died last night at 9:40pm

1326
01:44:54,660 --> 01:44:58,760
享年八十一岁
The Pope was 81 years old

1327
01:44:58,770 --> 01:45:04,700
教皇在过去几个月一直受病痛折磨
and had been in poor health for the last several months

1328
01:45:10,040 --> 01:45:11,710
康妮
Connie

1329
01:45:13,280 --> 01:45:18,510
我这一辈子都在力争上游
all my life I, kept trying to go up in society

1330
01:45:18,520 --> 01:45:22,750
希望成为一个干净清白的人
where everything higher up was legal, straight.

1331
01:45:23,260 --> 01:45:27,820
但是我爬得越高 世界就越险恶
But the higher I go, the crookeder it becomes.

1332
01:45:29,530 --> 01:45:31,990
这些事什么时候才能结束?
How in the hell does it end?

1333
01:45:40,870 --> 01:45:44,370
千百年来人类相互残杀
Killing each other for centuries here.

1334
01:45:45,580 --> 01:45:47,440
为钱
For money

1335
01:45:47,450 --> 01:45:51,310
为名 为家族
for pride, for family.

1336
01:45:52,920 --> 01:45:57,880
为了免于沦为富贵者的奴隶
To keep from becoming the slaves of the rich pezzonovante.

1337
01:46:04,030 --> 01:46:06,890
我做了告解 康妮
I made confession, Connie.

1338
01:46:07,170 --> 01:46:10,260
坦白了我的罪行
I confessed my sins.

1339
01:46:10,900 --> 01:46:13,630
为什么 麦克? 这可不像你的作风
Why Michael, that's not like you.

1340
01:46:13,640 --> 01:46:17,130
何必向一个陌生人坦白罪行
You don't have to confess your sins to a stranger.

1341
01:46:17,140 --> 01:46:19,210
这个人不一样
It was the man.

1342
01:46:19,850 --> 01:46:22,140
他是个好人
A good man.

1343
01:46:22,150 --> 01:46:24,350
真正的神父
A true priest.

1344
01:46:27,490 --> 01:46:29,810
他可以改变事物
He changed things.

1345
01:46:31,990 --> 01:46:34,230
麦克
Michael

1346
01:46:34,860 --> 01:46:36,820
你知道
you know

1347
01:46:36,830 --> 01:46:39,760
有时候我会想起弗雷多
sometimes I think of poor Fredo

1348
01:46:39,770 --> 01:46:42,230
淹死在湖里
drowned.

1349
01:46:42,240 --> 01:46:44,260
那是天意
It was God's will.

1350
01:46:45,570 --> 01:46:48,400
是个可怕的意外
It was a terrible accident.

1351
01:46:49,140 --> 01:46:51,570
但这已经过去了
But it's finished.

1352
01:46:56,420 --> 01:46:58,810
麦克 我爱你
Michael, I love you.

1353
01:47:00,420 --> 01:47:03,810
我永远都会在你这边
I'll always help you.

1354
01:47:14,730 --> 01:47:17,000
康妮
Connie.

1355
01:47:46,230 --> 01:47:49,060
艾图贝洛阁下 太荣幸了
I am honored, Don Altobello

1356
01:47:49,070 --> 01:47:53,930
你还从巴勒摩来探望我
that you've come from Palermo to visit me.

1357
01:47:57,710 --> 01:48:02,370
这孩子长大了
Hey, the little kid! He's grown.

1358
01:48:02,380 --> 01:48:05,080
学毛驴给我看
Do the donkey for me.

1359
01:48:21,470 --> 01:48:24,030
离我们当初一起做买卖
It's been some time

1360
01:48:24,040 --> 01:48:27,130
已经很久了
since we did business together.

1361
01:48:29,410 --> 01:48:30,970
套句美国话
You are my 'ace in the hole'

1362
01:48:30,980 --> 01:48:34,470
你是我盖着的王牌
as we say in America.

1363
01:48:34,680 --> 01:48:37,970
我有个麻烦
I have a stone in my shoe.

1364
01:48:37,980 --> 01:48:41,520
你能帮我除掉
You can remove it.

1365
01:48:47,730 --> 01:48:50,390
只有一个麻烦?
Only one stone?

1366
01:48:52,830 --> 01:48:56,530
这一个就很危险
It's dangerous.

1367
01:48:56,540 --> 01:48:58,660
大名鼎鼎的人物
A famous man.

1368
01:48:58,670 --> 01:49:03,410
你要格外小心
You will have to take precautions.

1369
01:49:05,040 --> 01:49:07,770
要我做什么你说
Tell me what to do.

1370
01:49:07,780 --> 01:49:11,520
然后我会开价
Then I will tell you my price.

1371
01:49:15,790 --> 01:49:18,220
面包极品!
Ah, what bread!

1372
01:49:21,690 --> 01:49:24,430
橄榄油
Ah, olive oil

1373
01:49:29,100 --> 01:49:30,690
无杂味
virgin

1374
01:49:30,700 --> 01:49:33,300
西西里独有
only in Sicily

1375
01:49:35,240 --> 01:49:36,930
敬你!
A salute!

1376
01:49:36,940 --> 01:49:39,180
敬敌人!
A morte!

1377
01:49:52,730 --> 01:49:54,290
凯!
Kay!

1378
01:49:54,490 --> 01:49:56,490
康妮! 你好吗?
Oh, Connie! How are you?

1379
01:49:56,730 --> 01:49:59,400
玛莉 好想你!
Mary, I've missed you!

1380
01:50:00,330 --> 01:50:02,490
- 麦克 你好 - 你好 凯
- Well, hello Michael. - Hello Kay.

1381
01:50:02,500 --> 01:50:04,390
妈 你看
Mom, look at this.

1382
01:50:04,400 --> 01:50:08,130
"乡间骑士"

1383
01:50:08,140 --> 01:50:10,400
可惜道格拉斯不能来
You know it's too bad that Douglas couldn't be with us.

1384
01:50:10,410 --> 01:50:12,250
他很想来
No, no, I know. He wanted to come very much,

1385
01:50:12,260 --> 01:50:14,340
可是有重要的官司
but he had a very important trial.

1386
01:50:14,350 --> 01:50:16,580
我知道他一定想来
I know he wanted to come.

1387
01:50:21,390 --> 01:50:25,450
现在 你儿子是个艺术家了 嗯?
Well, your son's an artist, huh?

1388
01:50:25,460 --> 01:50:28,150
是啊应该谢谢你
Oh yes. Thanks to you.

1389
01:50:28,160 --> 01:50:29,830
谢什么?
Oh, what for?

1390
01:50:30,200 --> 01:50:32,990
谢你逼我放他走
For making me, let him go.

1391
01:50:33,330 --> 01:50:34,790
这样啊
Oh.

1392
01:50:34,800 --> 01:50:36,290
这么多年了
After all these years

1393
01:50:36,300 --> 01:50:38,530
我第一次来西西里
here I am in Sicily for the first time.

1394
01:50:38,540 --> 01:50:40,900
我帮你们照相
I want to get a picture of you together.

1395
01:50:43,740 --> 01:50:45,700
爸 微笑
Hey dad, smile.

1396
01:50:49,980 --> 01:50:53,840
纳利还在你身边 为什么?
I see you still have Al Neri. Why?

1397
01:50:54,090 --> 01:50:58,380
我需要他啊他可以扶我上下车
Well, I need him. He helps me get in and out of the car.

1398
01:50:58,790 --> 01:51:00,790
帮我提公事包
Carry my briefcase.

1399
01:51:00,890 --> 01:51:03,160
你还在撒谎
You're still a liar Michael.

1400
01:51:04,000 --> 01:51:07,490
我来带你看看真正的西西里
Let me show you Sicily. The real Sicily.

1401
01:51:07,500 --> 01:51:10,090
这样也许你能更了解我们家的历史
Maybe you'll understand the family history a little better.

1402
01:51:10,100 --> 01:51:12,960
我了解的已经够多的了
Oh I think I understand it well enough.

1403
01:51:41,970 --> 01:51:43,830
拿着
Take them.

1404
01:52:04,620 --> 01:52:06,280
安东尼
Anthony

1405
01:52:06,290 --> 01:52:11,860
这是多年前你做给我的
I have something you made for me a very long time ago

1406
01:52:12,330 --> 01:52:14,860
它会给你带来好运
It may bring you luck.

1407
01:52:19,140 --> 01:52:20,760
你留下来了?
You saved it, huh?

1408
01:52:20,770 --> 01:52:22,900
- 你还记得吗? - 记得
- Remember? - I remember.

1409
01:52:26,680 --> 01:52:28,410
谢谢你 爸爸
Thank you dad.

1410
01:52:30,050 --> 01:52:31,780
我为你骄傲
I'm proud of you.

1411
01:52:32,450 --> 01:52:33,950
谢谢
Thank you.

1412
01:52:50,040 --> 01:52:52,190
他们的身手靠得住吗?
Are they as good as they look?

1413
01:52:52,200 --> 01:52:55,470
当然 一流高手
They're better. They're the best.

1414
01:52:55,610 --> 01:52:58,230
有他们在 麦克叔一定安全
As long as they're around, Uncle Michael is safe.

1415
01:52:58,240 --> 01:53:00,510
再见
Bye.

1416
01:53:02,380 --> 01:53:04,010
再见 告诉你爸我回来吃晚饭
Bye. Tell your father I'll be back for dinner.

1417
01:53:04,020 --> 01:53:05,210
好的
Okay.

1418
01:53:05,850 --> 01:53:06,980
玩儿的开心点
Have fun.

1419
01:53:06,990 --> 01:53:08,680
告诉安东尼等我
And tell Tony to be sure to wait for me.

1420
01:53:08,690 --> 01:53:10,510
好的
Okay. I will.

1421
01:53:11,520 --> 01:53:12,650
再见 妈妈
Bye mom.

1422
01:53:12,660 --> 01:53:16,620
早上好 夫人 请吩咐
Buon giorno, Signora. At your service

1423
01:53:20,300 --> 01:53:23,730
我见到爸爸会告诉他你走了
If I see dad, I'll tell him you left

1424
01:53:28,570 --> 01:53:33,280
像我父亲那样强大的人 在这个家族里只剩下你了
You are the only one left in this family with my father's strength.

1425
01:53:34,450 --> 01:53:38,580
假如麦克出事 我要你还击
If anything happens to Michael, I want you to strike back.

1426
01:53:41,450 --> 01:53:44,420
我会准备得妥妥当当
I'll have everything ready.

1427
01:53:46,930 --> 01:53:48,820
你发誓?
You swear?

1428
01:53:56,070 --> 01:53:57,890
我发誓
I swear to you.

1429
01:54:28,070 --> 01:54:34,430
我父亲就是在这里出生
Here it is. The house where my father was born.

1430
01:54:35,170 --> 01:54:37,300
他们来到这里
This is where they came

1431
01:54:37,310 --> 01:54:42,010
掳走还是孩子的他 想把他杀掉
to take him when he was a boy. To kill him.

1432
01:54:43,850 --> 01:54:45,780
等等
Wait.

1433
01:54:46,320 --> 01:54:48,250
你听
Listen to that.

1434
01:55:07,340 --> 01:55:09,940
玛莉恋爱了
You know, Mary's in love.

1435
01:55:10,840 --> 01:55:12,670
是 我知道
Yes, I know.

1436
01:55:13,710 --> 01:55:18,680
是一个黑眼睛的英俊意大利男人
With a handsome young Italian man. Dark eyes.

1437
01:55:19,020 --> 01:55:21,150
我不允许这事
I won't allow it

1438
01:55:23,520 --> 01:55:25,190
这是错误的
It's wrong.

1439
01:55:25,290 --> 01:55:27,720
错误而且危险
It's wrong and it's dangerous.

1440
01:55:27,730 --> 01:55:30,890
父亲 我的父亲!
Oh father, my father!

1441
01:55:30,900 --> 01:55:33,790
给我一点时间向主祈祷
Give me some time to pray to the Lord.

1442
01:55:33,800 --> 01:55:37,230
卡里尼男爵夫人不贞
The Baroness of Carini had betrayed her husband

1443
01:55:37,240 --> 01:55:41,530
同她的堂兄相恋
and fallen in love with her cousin.

1444
01:55:41,540 --> 01:55:45,280
不可饶恕!
There will be no forgiveness!

1445
01:55:46,080 --> 01:55:48,470
她父亲举起宝剑
Her father stabbed her

1446
01:55:48,480 --> 01:55:52,740
将她一剑穿心!
through the heart!

1447
01:55:59,690 --> 01:56:01,480
为了家庭的名声吗
Honor, huh?

1448
01:56:20,910 --> 01:56:24,140
我还记得当年你去见我父母
You know, I remember the time that you came to my parent's house.

1449
01:56:24,150 --> 01:56:26,050
你把我带进房里
And you took me into that room.

1450
01:56:26,060 --> 01:56:28,110
告诉我你的家族生意
And you told me about the family business

1451
01:56:28,120 --> 01:56:31,010
说你决不会沾手
and how you were never going to have anything to do with it.

1452
01:56:31,020 --> 01:56:33,650
那口气就像安东尼
You sounded like Tony

1453
01:56:33,660 --> 01:56:35,930
当年的我的确很像
I was a lot like Tony.

1454
01:56:44,570 --> 01:56:46,060
- 这里 凯 - 什么?
- And there we see it. Kay. - What?

1455
01:56:46,240 --> 01:56:47,360
你来开车好吗?
you mind driving?

1456
01:56:47,370 --> 01:56:48,830
出什么事了吗?
No, what's wrong.

1457
01:56:48,840 --> 01:56:51,910
我的眼睛有时侯还好 有时候就...
My eyes. Sometimes they're all right. But...

1458
01:56:53,710 --> 01:56:55,540
还有 我要去见汤马仙奴阁下
Listen, I have to see Don Tommasino

1459
01:56:55,550 --> 01:56:57,110
你好 夫人
Benday, signora.

1460
01:57:02,220 --> 01:57:04,150
看来今天没有随身保镖跟着啊
There's no bodyguards today.

1461
01:57:04,190 --> 01:57:06,010
我可是真的偷跑出来的
I really snuck away.

1462
01:57:12,900 --> 01:57:20,330
神父 上哪儿去? 要搭便车吗?
Father, where are you going? Would you like a ride?"

1463
01:57:26,950 --> 01:57:29,240
我认得你
I know you.

1464
01:57:29,250 --> 01:57:31,940
你是孟太利家的莫斯卡
You're Mosca of Montelepre.

1465
01:57:31,950 --> 01:57:33,680
以前当过杀手
You were an assassin then

1466
01:57:33,690 --> 01:57:35,840
现在也是
and you're an assassin now

1467
01:57:35,850 --> 01:57:39,880
我知道麦克·柯里昂在你家
I know Michael Corleone is at your house.

1468
01:57:39,890 --> 01:57:42,130
我会跟着你进去
I will pass through the gates with you.

1469
01:57:59,040 --> 01:58:00,370
卡罗 你好吗?
How are you?

1470
01:58:00,550 --> 01:58:02,250
这是卡罗 我的老朋友
Kay, this is Calo, my old friend.

1471
01:58:02,260 --> 01:58:04,280
以前的保镖
One of my bodyguards in the old days.

1472
01:58:09,860 --> 01:58:12,380
- 我们可以在这里等他 - 要喝一杯吗?
- We can wait here. - You want drink?

1473
01:58:12,390 --> 01:58:13,920
好的 我们进去?
Yeah. Shall we go?

1474
01:58:17,860 --> 01:58:20,790
我以前在这里度过了很长时间
I spent a lot of time in this room

1475
01:58:21,930 --> 01:58:23,930
想念你
thinking of you.

1476
01:58:27,010 --> 01:58:28,770
然后你结婚了
And then you got married.

1477
01:58:32,910 --> 01:58:34,640
但我依然想念你
I still thought of you.

1478
01:58:35,310 --> 01:58:37,140
那间房里有什么?
What's in that room?

1479
01:58:40,990 --> 01:58:43,510
麦克 你知道来这里很危险
You know this is dangerous for you, Michael.

1480
01:58:43,520 --> 01:58:45,450
这儿是西西里
This is Sicily.

1481
01:58:47,590 --> 01:58:49,120
我爱这里
I love this country.

1482
01:58:49,130 --> 01:58:50,890
为什么?
Why?

1483
01:58:52,600 --> 01:58:56,190
世代以来
Well, all through history

1484
01:58:56,200 --> 01:58:59,460
这里的人受尽折磨
terrible things have happened to these people.

1485
01:58:59,470 --> 01:59:02,430
各种不公正的事
Terrible injustice.

1486
01:59:02,770 --> 01:59:05,870
但是他们依旧期待
But they still expect good

1487
01:59:05,880 --> 01:59:08,170
会有好的事情发生
rather than bad will happen to them.

1488
01:59:08,180 --> 01:59:10,540
就像我和你
Sort of like me and you, huh?

1489
01:59:14,250 --> 01:59:15,340
哪里?
How so?

1490
01:59:15,350 --> 01:59:17,280
我现在在这里啊
Well I'm still here, right?

1491
01:59:17,820 --> 01:59:20,120
我们的过去也不很愉快
We do have a bad history

1492
01:59:20,130 --> 01:59:21,350
但我还在这里
but I'm still here.

1493
01:59:21,360 --> 01:59:24,490
是的 你还在 但是心里只有恐惧
Oh yes you are. But with dread.

1494
01:59:28,630 --> 01:59:30,960
说出你的心意!
Gimme the order! C'mon!

1495
01:59:30,970 --> 01:59:34,360
为什么要这么做? 让我不怕你?
What's that supposed to do, is that supposed to make me not dread you?

1496
01:59:36,440 --> 01:59:38,970
我们来这里是为了看歌剧
We're in Sicily, the opera.

1497
01:59:41,180 --> 01:59:42,640
好吧
Okay

1498
01:59:45,080 --> 01:59:47,320
现在干什么?
what do we do now?

1499
01:59:49,790 --> 01:59:51,720
讲道理
Be reasonable.

1500
01:59:52,360 --> 01:59:54,450
我希望我们不要再伤害彼此
Let's try not to hurt each other.

1501
02:00:01,330 --> 02:00:03,660
我希望你能原谅我
I want you to forgive me.

1502
02:00:06,240 --> 02:00:08,100
原谅你什么?
For what?

1503
02:00:08,510 --> 02:00:10,400
所有事情
Everything.

1504
02:00:13,050 --> 02:00:16,640
像上帝那样?
Oh, like God, huh?

1505
02:00:16,850 --> 02:00:20,610
不用那么夸张
Oh, I, I need something a little closer.

1506
02:00:22,420 --> 02:00:26,890
你当时不了解我的处境
You couldn't understand, back in those days.

1507
02:00:27,090 --> 02:00:29,220
我爱我的父亲
I love my father

1508
02:00:29,230 --> 02:00:32,190
我曾经发誓不会成为他那样的人
I swore I would never be, a man like him

1509
02:00:32,200 --> 02:00:34,990
但是我爱他 而他又身处险境
but I loved him. And he was in danger

1510
02:00:35,000 --> 02:00:36,590
我能怎么办?
what could I do?

1511
02:00:36,600 --> 02:00:40,160
然后 你也身处险境
And then later, you were in danger.

1512
02:00:40,170 --> 02:00:44,140
孩子也一样 我能怎么办?
Our children, were in danger. what could I do?

1513
02:00:44,540 --> 02:00:51,580
你们是我在这个世界上最重要的人
You were all that I loved, valued, most in the world.

1514
02:00:52,320 --> 02:00:55,580
但是我正在 已经失去了你
And, I'm losing you, I lost you, anyway.

1515
02:00:55,590 --> 02:00:57,750
你离开了我
You're gone.

1516
02:00:58,590 --> 02:01:00,920
我失去了一切
and it was all for nothing

1517
02:01:00,930 --> 02:01:03,130
所以
so

1518
02:01:06,100 --> 02:01:12,170
你要理解 我之后的人生都是注定的
you have to understand, I had a whole different destiny planned.

1519
02:01:14,770 --> 02:01:16,770
好吧 我不说了
All right, I'll stop.

1520
02:01:27,220 --> 02:01:29,210
麦克 我不知道你到底要我怎么做
I really don't konw what you want from me,Michael.

1521
02:01:29,220 --> 02:01:31,420
我真的不知道
I really don't know.

1522
02:01:31,590 --> 02:01:33,380
我是说
I mean

1523
02:01:33,390 --> 02:01:37,150
我并不是你想像的那种人
I'm not the man that you think I am.

1524
02:01:37,560 --> 02:01:39,920
我不知道
I dont't know.

1525
02:01:39,930 --> 02:01:42,100
我爱你 凯
I love you, Kay.

1526
02:01:42,870 --> 02:01:46,540
不要再害怕我
Don't dread me, anymore.

1527
02:01:50,740 --> 02:01:56,710
其实 在这里的每个晚上
You know, every night here in Sicily

1528
02:01:56,720 --> 02:01:59,010
我作梦
I dream

1529
02:01:59,790 --> 02:02:03,150
梦见我的妻子和孩子
about my wife and my children.

1530
02:02:05,320 --> 02:02:08,490
梦见我如何失去他们
And how I lost them.

1531
02:02:09,430 --> 02:02:16,460
如果这对你是种安慰我想告诉你
I guess, if it's any consolation, I want you to know that

1532
02:02:18,670 --> 02:02:24,170
麦克 过去我一直爱你
I always loved you, Michael.

1533
02:02:24,940 --> 02:02:32,620
以后是一样
I always, I always will.

1534
02:02:59,110 --> 02:03:00,810
出什么事了?
What is it? What's wrong?

1535
02:03:02,050 --> 02:03:06,410
汤马西诺阁下被人枪杀了
They found Don Tommasino shot.

1536
02:03:06,420 --> 02:03:08,150
他死了?
Is he dead?

1537
02:03:10,220 --> 02:03:14,250
我家主人死了 血债血偿
My master is dead. Blood calls for blood.

1538
02:03:14,260 --> 02:03:18,930
我一定要报仇
I must have revenge

1539
02:03:20,570 --> 02:03:26,490
将来也许有难事要你去办
Some day, you may have to do a difficult service for me.

1540
02:03:26,500 --> 02:03:30,210
尽管吩咐
Command me.

1541
02:03:31,140 --> 02:03:34,430
我会为他报仇
I will avenge him

1542
02:03:48,430 --> 02:03:50,350
计票
Totals

1543
02:03:51,960 --> 02:03:55,160
罗舒达 一票
Lorscheider, 1 vote.

1544
02:03:55,270 --> 02:03:58,860
塞里 十一票
Siri, 11 votes.

1545
02:03:58,870 --> 02:04:03,160
龙巴度 九十九票
Lamberto, 99 votes.

1546
02:04:07,750 --> 02:04:11,210
你是否接受推举
Do you accept your election

1547
02:04:11,220 --> 02:04:13,680
担任教皇圣职?
as supreme pontiff?

1548
02:04:13,690 --> 02:04:19,950
上帝明鉴 赐福吾同僚之决策
My God, shed light on the decision they have taken on my behalf

1549
02:04:20,060 --> 02:04:22,050
我接受
I accept.

1550
02:04:22,060 --> 02:04:24,690
你希望被如何称呼?
By what name do you wish to be called?

1551
02:04:24,700 --> 02:04:28,400
若望保禄一世
John Paul the First.

1552
02:04:57,860 --> 02:05:00,060
我将即刻执行此事
I will do things 'right away'

1553
02:05:00,070 --> 02:05:04,290
而不再考量拖延
rather than in 'a little while.'

1554
02:05:04,300 --> 02:05:07,870
梵蒂冈会计师凯斯济
Frederik Keinszig, known for a decade as "God's banker,"

1555
02:05:07,880 --> 02:05:11,730
已失踪三天 最后被见于
has been reported missing.He was last seen three days ago,

1556
02:05:11,740 --> 02:05:14,350
梵蒂冈辖下
leaving the Rome offices of the Vatican owned

1557
02:05:14,360 --> 02:05:17,170
"屹立"的罗马办公室内
corporation International Immobiliare.

1558
02:05:17,180 --> 02:05:21,040
随之失踪的还有大笔款项 及多份文件
Also missing was a large sum of money, and several documents.

1559
02:05:21,050 --> 02:05:25,950
凯斯济快接电话啊白痴
Come on, Keinszig, you fool.

1560
02:05:27,660 --> 02:05:29,720
凯斯济的失踪
Mr. Keinszig's absence

1561
02:05:29,730 --> 02:05:32,720
使得梵蒂冈银行的交易越显蹊跷
casts further suspicion on the dealings of the Vatican bank.

1562
02:05:32,730 --> 02:05:35,690
多年以来该行及其下属子公司
For several years the bank and its subsidiary companies

1563
02:05:35,700 --> 02:05:37,450
都被指控进行
have been the object of allegations of

1564
02:05:37,460 --> 02:05:41,400
进行非法交易
disreputable business practices.

1565
02:05:41,410 --> 02:05:46,040
鲁加西 请你尽量要了解
Lucchesi, will you please try and understand.

1566
02:05:46,780 --> 02:05:48,640
我打电话找过他
I have phoned him.

1567
02:05:48,650 --> 02:05:51,210
也一直在等他的电话
I have waited here by the phone.

1568
02:05:54,050 --> 02:05:58,110
你一定要记住鲁西尼
You would do well to remember, Mr. Lucchesi

1569
02:05:58,120 --> 02:06:00,680
当今教皇的想法
that this Pope

1570
02:06:00,690 --> 02:06:05,860
与其上任大为不同
has very, different ideas from the last one.

1571
02:06:26,990 --> 02:06:29,550
再见 老朋友
Goodbye my old friend.

1572
02:06:31,560 --> 02:06:34,150
你本可以多活几年
You could have lived a little longer

1573
02:06:35,190 --> 02:06:38,660
我也可以更接近我的理想
I could be closer to my dream.

1574
02:06:43,940 --> 02:06:47,070
汤马西诺阁下 你深受爱戴
You were so loved, Don Tommasino.

1575
02:06:51,510 --> 02:06:54,000
为什么我招人畏惧
Why was I so feared

1576
02:06:54,010 --> 02:06:56,300
你却受人爱戴?
and you so loved?

1577
02:06:56,510 --> 02:06:58,580
是什么原因?
What was it?

1578
02:06:59,150 --> 02:07:01,880
我也做过不少好事
I was no less honorable.

1579
02:07:03,530 --> 02:07:06,390
我也想做好人
I wanted to do good.

1580
02:07:09,670 --> 02:07:10,970
到底是什么背弃了我?
What betrayed me?

1581
02:07:10,980 --> 02:07:14,040
我的想法? 还是我的心?
My mind? My heart?

1582
02:07:15,580 --> 02:07:18,970
为什么我要逼迫我自己呢?
Why do I condemn myself so?

1583
02:07:24,720 --> 02:07:26,910
我发誓
I swear

1584
02:07:26,920 --> 02:07:30,190
以我子女的性命发誓
on the lives of my children

1585
02:07:33,670 --> 02:07:37,960
给我赎罪的机会
Give me a chance to redeem myself

1586
02:07:40,340 --> 02:07:45,080
我再也不会犯下罪行
and I will sin, no more.

1587
02:08:08,070 --> 02:08:11,030
你脸色不好 有坏消息
You look pale. Bad news.

1588
02:08:11,040 --> 02:08:12,800
告诉我
Tell me right away

1589
02:08:14,010 --> 02:08:16,710
现在不仅是银行舞弊
It's not just a bad banking deal.

1590
02:08:17,740 --> 02:08:20,010
这些人就是屠夫
These guys are butchers.

1591
02:08:20,880 --> 02:08:22,840
哪些人?
What guys?

1592
02:08:22,850 --> 02:08:24,740
鲁加西
Lucchesi.

1593
02:08:25,380 --> 02:08:26,910
他控制了所有人
He controls all of them

1594
02:08:26,920 --> 02:08:28,610
包括老艾
Altobello,

1595
02:08:28,620 --> 02:08:30,750
大主教
the Archbishop

1596
02:08:31,160 --> 02:08:34,150
还有其他更高的人
other people higher up, P2, maybe

1597
02:08:34,160 --> 02:08:36,180
还有秘密不知道
Secret, unknown.

1598
02:08:36,190 --> 02:08:38,330
他们正在做什么事情
They're running things.

1599
02:08:40,770 --> 02:08:42,430
我是他们的障碍
I'm in their way.

1600
02:08:43,570 --> 02:08:46,190
他雇了职业杀手要杀你
He's hired a professional assassin to kill you.

1601
02:08:46,200 --> 02:08:47,800
是西西里人
He's Sicilian.

1602
02:08:47,810 --> 02:08:49,800
不知道名字
I don't know his name,

1603
02:08:50,880 --> 02:08:53,140
据说他从没有失手过
but they say he never fails.

1604
02:08:54,350 --> 02:08:56,610
我们都很危险
Then no one is safe.

1605
02:08:59,280 --> 02:09:02,550
新教皇的处境也很危险
Even the new pope is in danger.

1606
02:09:02,990 --> 02:09:07,350
我们还来得及阻止
We still have time. We can prevent this.

1607
02:09:11,200 --> 02:09:13,090
我尽力了
I tried

1608
02:09:15,630 --> 02:09:17,900
我已经尽力
I tried

1609
02:09:18,700 --> 02:09:21,840
想避免走到这田地
to keep everything from coming to this.

1610
02:09:21,875 --> 02:09:24,570
但是躲不开
But it's not possible,

1611
02:09:24,580 --> 02:09:27,780
在世上躲不开
not in this world.

1612
02:09:27,880 --> 02:09:30,310
下命令吧
Give me the order.

1613
02:09:33,380 --> 02:09:35,680
那你就没有回头路了
You won't be able to go back.

1614
02:09:36,750 --> 02:09:38,410
你会步我的后尘
You'll be like me.

1615
02:09:38,420 --> 02:09:40,190
好啊
Good.

1616
02:09:40,690 --> 02:09:43,550
我一辈子都想脱离江湖
All my life I wanted out.

1617
02:09:43,560 --> 02:09:47,020
希望我的家庭远离是非
I wanted the family out.

1618
02:09:47,670 --> 02:09:50,120
我不想
Well, I don't want out.

1619
02:09:50,130 --> 02:09:52,990
我渴望拥有保护这个家族声誉的权利
I want the power to preserve the family.

1620
02:09:57,480 --> 02:10:00,300
下命令吧
I'm asking for the order.

1621
02:10:20,600 --> 02:10:22,490
行了
It's done.

1622
02:10:23,900 --> 02:10:26,830
我干不下去了
Because I can't do it anymore.

1623
02:10:31,010 --> 02:10:32,470
没关系
Well, it doesn't matter.

1624
02:10:32,480 --> 02:10:35,870
文森会处理的 出去吧
Vincent knows what to do. Come on outside.

1625
02:10:35,880 --> 02:10:39,510
歇会儿 不要再想了
Take a rest and don't think about it.

1626
02:10:39,520 --> 02:10:41,110
我能做的就是一直思考
All I do is think about it.

1627
02:10:41,120 --> 02:10:43,110
我就是你的儿子
I'm your son.

1628
02:10:43,590 --> 02:10:46,150
一切交给我
Command me in all things.

1629
02:10:47,960 --> 02:10:50,590
放弃我女儿
Give up my daughter.

1630
02:10:52,900 --> 02:10:55,260
这是你要付的代价
That's the price you pay

1631
02:10:56,170 --> 02:10:58,700
为你选择的人生
for the life you choose.

1632
02:11:24,730 --> 02:11:26,430
侄子
Nephew

1633
02:11:28,430 --> 02:11:30,930
从今以后
from this moment on

1634
02:11:32,170 --> 02:11:34,990
你就是文森柯里昂
call yourself Vincent Corleone.

1635
02:11:39,540 --> 02:11:42,840
坐下
Sit.

1636
02:11:56,060 --> 02:11:57,990
文森阁下
Vincenzo.

1637
02:11:59,900 --> 02:12:01,820
康妮 谢谢
Grazie Connie.

1638
02:12:03,500 --> 02:12:05,530
柯阁下
Don Corleone.

1639
02:12:08,610 --> 02:12:11,530
文森柯里昂阁下!
Don Vincenzo Corleone.

1640
02:12:59,720 --> 02:13:01,080
玛莉
Mary.

1641
02:13:24,150 --> 02:13:26,750
"乡间骑士"歌剧

1642
02:13:44,500 --> 02:13:47,030
文森
Et Tu, Vincenzo

1643
02:13:47,040 --> 02:13:50,000
你对麦克的感情我了解
I know how you feel about Michael

1644
02:13:50,010 --> 02:13:52,470
但你救不了他
but you, you can't save him.

1645
02:13:52,480 --> 02:13:54,610
他失败了
He's lost.

1646
02:13:55,450 --> 02:13:57,980
为自己打算吧
Think of yourself.

1647
02:13:58,420 --> 02:14:01,280
你的答案是什么?
What's your answer, Vincent?

1648
02:14:02,890 --> 02:14:05,380
欣赏歌剧
Enjoy the opera.

1649
02:14:06,720 --> 02:14:08,920
一切都安排妥当
It's all taken care of.

1650
02:14:14,130 --> 02:14:16,900
察看一下酒吧 我去检查屋顶
Check the bar. I'll check the top floor.

1651
02:14:20,710 --> 02:14:23,830
但愿安东尼在台上演唱
Here's hoping Tony sings better at Theatre Maximo

1652
02:14:23,840 --> 02:14:25,540
胜过他在洗澡时的歌声
than he does in the shower.

1653
02:14:27,580 --> 02:14:30,140
亲爱的康妮
My darling, Constanzia.

1654
02:14:30,210 --> 02:14:32,010
艾图贝洛阁下
Oh, Don Altobello.

1655
02:14:32,020 --> 02:14:33,770
这真是件大事
This is a great occasion.

1656
02:14:33,780 --> 02:14:35,640
来 坐
Come and sit down.

1657
02:14:39,560 --> 02:14:41,620
生日快乐
Happy birthday.

1658
02:14:41,830 --> 02:14:44,390
八十岁的人看来像六十
You're eighty years old.You don't look more than sixty.

1659
02:14:44,400 --> 02:14:46,650
我的生日只有你记得
You're the only one who remembered.

1660
02:14:46,660 --> 02:14:48,430
刚得到的消息
Michael, we just got the word.

1661
02:14:48,440 --> 02:14:50,360
"屹立"的交易教皇签署了
The Pope's ratified the Immobiliare deal.

1662
02:14:50,370 --> 02:14:51,830
我们赢了
We've won.

1663
02:14:51,840 --> 02:14:53,730
恭喜
Congratulations.

1664
02:14:56,470 --> 02:14:58,970
世事的发展还真是奇妙
How strange, the way things work.

1665
02:14:58,980 --> 02:15:00,800
正如你所预言的
The Pope's doing exactly what you said he'd do

1666
02:15:00,810 --> 02:15:02,510
教皇清理门户了
he's cleaning house.

1667
02:15:03,450 --> 02:15:05,770
他应该谨慎
He should be careful.

1668
02:15:05,780 --> 02:15:07,710
做诚实的人也会有危险
It's dangerous to be an honest man.

1669
02:15:14,330 --> 02:15:17,250
